{
  "stem": "151.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So this woman must have been in her 80's, hardly believed that she will never return.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I thought to myself, how cruel that they won't let her keep this little memoir.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And then she closed this locket and through the cracks of the cattle car, handed it to the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was just 19.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Si, let me tell you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The cattle cars opened and I believing that we're going to Germany to work was very eager to get a good job so that I could help out my parents and my little sister so that they don't have to work so hard.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was a strong, healthy athlete so I knew I can work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was going to save them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When I jumped off that cattle car and I looked around, I knew right away that we're doomed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "All I could see for miles and miles were barbed wires.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you know, so many feet there was always a tower, a wooden tower.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when I looked up there I saw this Nazi soldier behind the machine gun, pointing it at us, watching every move we were making.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "On the loudspeakers the Nazis were telling us to leave all our belongings behind, they are going to deliver it to us to the camp.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so I turned back to the cattle car and called my sister Clara, who came forward crying, rubbing her eye from the darkness into the light.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I grabbed her hand and I said to her, 'You hold on to me, no matter what happens.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You and I must stay together.' And she started to cry and she said, 'But Renee, let's wait for mom and dad.' And I turned back to the cattle car for mom and dad, they were gone.",
      "word_count": 37
    }
  ],
